author: Reuters
title: BRIEF-Precise Biometrics says its BioMatch Mobile integrated in new Chinese smartphone
text:
Sept 23 Precise Biometrics Ab
* Says its biomatch mobile integrated in new chinese smartphone
* Says the value of license revenue is based on the number of sensors FPC delivers to the mobile phone manufacturer and cannot be forecasted at this point Link to press release: here ,c9835138 Further company coverage: (Stockholm Newsroom)
